Dialogs.Dialog: Because... It seemed like you didn't...
Geez. Don't look like you're having fun.
Hey. You were telling me about something, but backed down.
I'm worried if you tell me something like that.
Because when you are interested in something... your eyes are shining.
It's too late. I'm not speaking about it, okay?
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Will you tell me about what you don't wanted to talk last time.
Yes.... You know? A man, after getting out of the bath...
Is walking around the house with one piece of underwear a good thing?
My friend was worried that her father didn't stop doing it, after telling him to.
I've never seen mine at home do that, so I couldn't give good advice...
Hey, can you do it somehow?
Do you remember about my friend who was worried about her father? I think I give up.
It's fasted to defend him. It seems that when her dad goes out of the bath, he should stay in his room.
...Hey, you do that too? Being in your underwear after taking a bath...
How know... Maybe. Well, I live alone, so I don't need to be careful... Right?
...Well then, I have to get used to it.
（How are you going to do that）
I wonder where everyone learns to do makeup.
Mama seems to have gone to a beauty school and taught in an extracurricular class.
Emm, that doesn't seem to be the case at our school.
Is that so... I'll ask someone next time.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, do you want to put on makeup?
I wonder if I should know a little. I want you to think I'm always cute...
...I won't be happy if you said it so lightly.
There are some girls in class who are very good at makeup.
That girl said that my face would look good with flashy makeup.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ with flashy makeup... Hmm, is that right?
Don't you want to see it?
I want to see it, is that okay?
Hmm... Shall I try? I'm kidding.
! If I say no... It's no...
But, you want to see it? Hey, tell me if you want to see?
What happened to the flashing make up Manaka? That story you were telling me before.
Yes. It was amazing... That was the first time...
Did you do that! Did you take a photo?
With that as a reference, I am practicing at home.
I want to master it and transform with my own power, before you see it.
Yes. That's why, can you wait a little?
...I'm sorry. Flashy makeup has been banned.
Papa saw me practicing... "It's not something high school students should do!" he said.
Yes. The magazine you referred me to, was also banned.
The hairstyle called "Mega" was amazing, so I imitated it. I asked Mama to help me....
My hair as a chocolate cornet and flashy makeup. Fufu, I got too bad.
Therefore, I'll try after graduating. Can you wait until then?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, did you go to the dentist?
Don't tell me that. Weren't you in pain the other day?
Geez, don't. That story is new to me.
（She tells me this... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, are afraid of dentists?）
Hey. Have you been to the dentist recently?
I used to go there when I was little... So I was wondering how is it like now.
What if your teeth hurt in the meantime?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you seem to brush your teeth properly.
I... I still can't forget that sound.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, I think your teeth are hurting...）
Ah... I'm sorry, I worried you.
Yes. I thought it was not good... So, I went to the dentist.
I see, I'm glad! How was it?
A scratch on the gums was the cause of the pain, not the caries.
A scratch on your gums? Why?
I was brushing my teeth, right? My hands slipped... I had too much momentum...
Ah, so that was it! That happens!
...I told you not to laugh. Geez, forget it!
Hey, do you know any interesting schools or lessons?
Hmm? Do you want to start something?
No. It's not me, It's Mama.
A lesson that mothers can enjoy...
I'd like something a little unusual that nobody does.
Hmm... If I think on something, I'll let you know.
Did you know? I found some lessons for Mama.
Yes. There were some strange things, but I didn't liked them very much.
I see. Was there something you wanted to try,▲高嶺＊＊▲?
What was it? Ah yes, a detective.
But it seems like a school rather than a lesson, so it seems impossible.
Ah, she ended up doing yoga.
I wonder if she would teach me the poses. Doesn't it sound fun?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, why don't you try it then?
Hmm... I don't care right now.
I will spend less time with you, and I don't like it.
Right? I'm kidding. But, wouldn't be nice if there were lessons two people could do?
Certainly... Would you like to try?
I investigated lessons two people can do together...
I see... I feel like an adult, somehow.
That's right. I mean, we play tennis already!
Ah... Fufu! Yes, isn't that right?
Then... Want to learn how to become an adult?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, what's wrong with your hand?
Yes... I cut my nails a bit too much.
I don't think it will affect me playing tennis or piano.
Fufu, do you want to confirm? Here.
If you talk to your friends about nails, why don't you do your nail?
Yes, that's right. Try wearing a glittery sticker.
Do you think so? Let's try it... But.
There are club activities, and piano lessons, and...
By the way ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Did you stop doing your nails?
Yes, I did. I can't make them shine, so I'm wondering if I can just clean them.
Yes, it's beautiful! A double circle!
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, with your nails that beautiful, you don't need stickers!）
Hey, do you remember my rival?
Ah, something related to ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s challenge games...
Yes. With that girl, I had a funny game of making funny faces last time.
Just staring at each other makes you laugh, right? You can make a lot of funny faces.
And how much you can make the other person laugh...
How is you funny face challenge going?
She's getting better and better. I want to fight back...
Yes. But I have no idea what to do.
Hmm. Isn't it the best strategy to imitate her?
That's difficult. Tell me what you mean.
...It's no use, because it's her attitude isn't something that can be taught, but stolen.
Maybe looking at the mirror in the bath... Maybe it'll be useful.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, is you funny faces practice going well?
I can do it better than before?
But she's a few steps higher, not so likely to win.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, it's amazing enough you can do that much...
Don't do it. If you become absorbed in it, I'll be in trouble.
But she belong to Manaka. I'm kidding.
By the way, do you keep playing funny faces?
No. It seems she got bored.
I see. I'm still interested in seeing you funny faces, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Fufu, you still don't have enough?
Yes. I'm sure there are still so many. I want you to see a lot of expressions.
That's right. I wonder when will you give up-.
It might take a lifetime, right?
I arrived a little late home. Mama protected me.
I was the one who was late.
Hmmー, being a father is hard.
But he's kind. It's not that serious, so don't worry, okay?
Living alone must be definitely tough...
Well, I find it comfortable ...Why do you ask?
No way, do you want to live alone?
I was just thinking it a little.
Haha, you don't need to do that▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Maybe, but sometimes I want to stretch my wings.
▲高嶺＊＊▲?... Don't tell me you were scolded by your father again.
Before was because you arrived a little late, what happened this time?
He found I was secretly watching a variety show.
Hey, did your father scold you again?
Especially now... Thank you for worrying.
It's just... It was tough before, but these days I feel it's a little different.
I would say that recently he's been a little unreasonable. I don't like that he doesn't makes sense.
I don't know. Papa seems to be a little less confident about scolding.
This never happened in the past.
I understand now why Papa has been scolding me unreasonably.
Well, Mama thought it was weird and asked him.
She said "I think you've been tough on Aika lately. Is something the matter".
A straight, strong Mom. And then?
Yes. When I get late after a date, make long phone calls, or send mails in the living room...He gets angry.
Fufu, it was refreshing. Thinking back, Papa seemed a little cute.
What would yo do it the wind was too strong to sleep?
Yes. So I wish to take measure from now on.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, but sometimes you can't sleep...
Geez. I couldn't sleep that time, and I was up until 12:00.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ certainly seems to be slow to sleep）
By the way, with what you told me before... How's your problem with the wind?
Emm... The bucket on the balcony on the second floor is gone.
Yes, but I'm glad I found it in the garden...
Something similar happened before, so it seems Mama was careful.
Yes. On a windy day, she used to hang the pillows on the roof, and they flung over to our neighbors.
It happened twice, then thrice... And, I think it'll happen again...
Yes... Mama has a forgetful personality.
I told you about my problems with the wind before, right?
Yes. Did you think about something?
Hmm... I thought something, but when I tried it, it failed.
Then, I was worried about the sound of my breathing...
I ended up staying up late, but I couldn't update the record.
I did something half-assed, now I have to finish it.
By the way, what happened to your measures against insomnia during strong winds?
Fufu, you say it so cool.
It's weird, you know? It seems like I'm used to it... I've been able to sleep normally, recently.
It's because... I feel like I'm becoming less sensitive...
Don't worry about it. You see, even if you were like that――.
Anyway, you're originally sober and insensitive.
Yes, did you know? There's a feeling of love with friends.
I heard that people though I was getting anxious recently, so I have been getting a lot of emails.
When I was talking about that, it looked like a lot of fun...
You say that, but you have a huge grin on your face, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Geez, I'm not grinning. But yes, it's something to grin about.
You told be about the kindness of your friends, how is it been going?
There're not only sending me mails, but talking with me on the phone.
Well, that's something to grin about.
Right? I feel like I'm receiving so much happiness.
Love is a wonderful thing, right? I'm glad I'm in love with you.
By the way, did your friends make any progress?
Well, I wonder if it could change dramatically.
Excuse me? I have a message from my friends to you.
It says "One day, W wants to have a date, so I'll ask for your support"
Ah, that's what they mean. Let the come to me!
Wouldn't it be nice if we could become their matchmakers?
That's right, maybe in a hurry. Fufu.
As we were saying before... What happened with the date with W?
Hmm... Isn't it a little later?
Ah, it was that. Even though I wanted to help.
But, my friend was very pleased with your reply, you know?
He was jealous of you, my reliable boyfriend.
Did you fall in love again?
Hey, do you grow a beard?
And what about your father's friends?
Whenever he comes back after drinking, he's thrilled about his beard.
So, I asked him why a man's beard was so stiff.
No. I wondered what it would look like if you had a beard.
Would you like to see me as a great man in a history textbook?
That kind of beard seems to be quite difficult, right?
That's right. But, you want to see it?
Well... Ah, a photo! Let's draw on it first! Right?
Did you try drawing the mustache, like we said?
Yes. I asked a friend who is good at it, and we made various versions.
As expected of you▲高嶺＊＊▲... It's nice...
I want to see the real one▼
Yes▼ Manaka would like to see you with one, okay?
Hey, can you look at this?
Imagining it, I really want to see it.
Yes, it looks good on you. Can you stay like that today?
Can I take a picture? I'll make it my treasure until I can see the real one▼
I'm sorry. Recently, it seems my battery is running low.
Until I started dating you, I didn't use my cell phone so much...
By the way, how's your battery been?
Yes... I was told I should buy a new battery, so I asked Papa but you know what he did?
He just turned his mouth sideways, and was silent.
I didn't even mention I was using it with you, right? He just ignored me.
Mama was fightened, even though she's usually calm.
And just like that, it's on hold.
But I won't run out of battery, so don't hesitate to call, okay?
It's about the conversation about your battery last time. Did you convince your father?
I didn't manage to convince Papa.
If I use it properly, I think the battery will last longer.
I see... Then, should we look how to make a battery last longer?
I got a new cell phone battery.
There is a service that replaces used batteries for free.
Well, I sneaked around. Mama laughed at me when she realized I was disobeying.
...You father is actually a kind guy.
Papa is always kind, isn't he? Kind and scary.
Emm... Well, I'm glad it worked out!
Thank you. I have to use it carefully from now on.
Huh? ▲高嶺＊＊▲, are you wearing something today?
Your perfume or something... it's different from usual.
...Ah~. Is it because I changed my conditioner?
Ah, I see. Yes, it's nice.
I'm glad you notice this little changes.
Especially you... My face might look weird, what should I do.
!? Uh, yes. I just brought a new one today.
You're glad I got it right?
Maybe! Don't miss even the smallest changes!
Ah~... I just remembered what I was happy about...
When I'm with you, I always feel like this.
? What's wrong? Why are you looking at me that much...
Hmm... You know? How should I say it...
I'm most happy you're able to notice things.
It feels like you're looking for mistakes, or...
No, I'm glad you care. Thank you.
Yes. I used my conditioner again.
Isn't it difficult to deal with girls?
Hey, if you notice things you don't like, can you tell me?
I'm sure there are many things, so I'll solve――.
Hey, I wonder why I have to study.
You see... a kid from my neighborhood asked me.
If I answered that it is because I was told that it would be really useful in the future...
Come to think of it, I just love studying... I couldn't say anything.
I wonder what should I answer if asked the same. Hmmー...
We spoke about why we should study, last time... I asked Mama too.
To expand our knowledge and to connect with other people.
But that's just Mama's reason, so I want to find out I want to study.
Yes. That's an opinion from an adult, right? I feel we have different reasons.
I can't concentrate in class because I've been thinking about all this now.
I want to find the answer quickly...
（If I lower my grades, I'll be in trouble）
I asked Papa why whe should study. He answered: So we don't regret it in the future.
When you try to that in back in school, after you become an adult, you can't do without courage and action.
Therefore, if you don't want to do it when you have to, you'll have to do it as an adult. That's the smart way.
I was stressed that there was regret in Papa's voice.
It seems he wasn't good enough. If he had time, he would had liked to continue studying.
After the clinic time is over, you may be late to study outside of your field?
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, if you don't study, you'll regret it... I see）
We spoke last time about why we should study. Have you met the kid who asked you?
No. But next time they ask, do you know what to answer?
I'll say "I don't know if everything will be useful as an adult".
Because, isn't it bad to lie?
But I don't know when it'll be needed, so be prepared.
Yes, I think I can finally enjoy studying after this.
A friend in class was playing a game and I had a look.
That's one thing I've been curious about that...
The boy who was the protagonist called himself "Ore-sama"... What do you think a girl should do?
Isn't it strange? Because if you don't know that, you can't empathize with her, right?
So I thought about it... Me-sama, it's funny... so Manaka-sama is okay?
We talked about the girl version of "Ore-sama" last time, right?
Did you think of something good?
My aunt and grandmother use it normally...
Mama says so in public places.
（Depends who and where you use it）
Last time we were speaking about "Ore-sama" and "Myself", didn't we?
I was interested, so I looked into it and found that there are many ways to do that.
Manaka Tanake here, I'm from the tennis club!
Uh... Can you forget about it? No? I won't do it anymore, okay?
Hey,▲高嶺＊＊▲. Last time we were talking about first- person pronuns.
Is it okay to make a request?
Yay! Then say it a little boyish.
It's a little different from what I thought.
Yes. Next... a little more boyish.
Hey, isn't it good like this? Let's end this.
... I was told it would be hard to have a popular boyfriend.
But, everyone is saying that, right?
And because you're so nice, how can't you be popular, right?
Hey. We spoke last time about how I was popular.
That's definitely a lie. It's because I'm with you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
How can you be so sure?
There's nothing I could do about it...
I wish I could hide you somewhere.
It's such a nice thing... No one is looking.
... Are you talking about my popularity? Was something different?
Yes. You're popular when we're together..
I see, that was it. Yes, that's right!
Huh? The misunderstanding was solved, why do you look like that?
We were talking about popularity last time, did you do something after?
Sorry for that time. I took everyone's joke and took a strange attitude...
Haha, it's okay. Anyway, it's good, this is over without problems.
Yes. From now on, stay the way you are, okay?
Please stay with me, only me▼
Of course! ▲高嶺＊＊▲, please stay only with me▼
Have you been making sweets recently?
What's wrong? Is there something you want to eat?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, if you make it, then anything is fine▼
Geez, you keep saying that. Anything is really okay?
It was a joke. You're so cute▼
（It's a bit refreshing to be teased by▲高嶺＊＊▲...）
How is your sweets making going?
Yes, I'm trying to do something strange but, it didn't go well...
▲高嶺＊＊▲, isn't this a normal thing?
I have the base taste, but I still feel like I'm missing something...
By the way, what are you making?
Don't worry, okay? It'll be delicious when finished.
You daid that anything would be fine, so I took the plunge.
How did the biscotti's turn out?
It seems those are Papa's favorite.
This are for Papa!, he said. Mama and me only had a little sample.
I'm sorry. Please wait until next time, okay?
Hmm? Didn't you like the nato biscottis?
Fufu! I'm sorry, I was being unfair.
▲高嶺＊＊▲... Do you find it fun to play around with me?
...Because when you're trouble, you look so cute.
I want to give you a hug. Can't I?
Can you sleep after a cup of coffe at night?
Hmmー, I wonder about it. Why?
A friend of Papa sent me coffee beans, which he said was delicious.
It has a very good scent and looks delicious...
Isn't it okay? Caffeine is used in tea.
Is that right? Yes... Shall we try it
（I feel like drinking it in the daytime... Well, that's okay）
That's right, how was the coffee you received?
Papa said I shouldn't drink it.
Yes. To tell you the truth, black tea is a no-go too, he said...
Yes... Perhaps it's delicious, so maybe he wants to keep it for himself.
We spoke about coffee before... Do you remember it?
Yes, when you told me how you father doesn't let you drink it, right?
Yes. I asked him "Is it bad because it's delicious?".
If you want to try it, drink it the day before your day off.
Please forgive me if I do.
Yes. But when I was told that, I was a little scared this time...
I wonder why. I don't want to be told what to do, or being told no. I'm acting like a child?
Oh. By the way... How was your coffee?
I tried it a while ago. Espresso, cafe au lait... and also black. It was delicious▼
Yes. Thanks to that, my eyes were wide open. I wasn't sleepy, even though it was bright outside...
Yes. So, is coffee good for a while?
But next time, I want to drink it with you. In the morning, because nights are troublesome, right?
Um... Did I say something strange?
Hey, does men also do diet?
I'm sure there are some who do. Why?
Yes. There's a large boy in my class...
It's uncommon, and it has become a hot topic among girls.
Because of him, it's a bit of a diet boom.
Should I also piggyback on it? ...I'm kidding.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲'s consciousness is wary of others...Hmm）
We were talking about diets before, right?
...Weren't you in the same class? What happened to that guy?
He has a favorite girl in the same class, and he's trying to confess to her.
Yes. When I heard it, I really wanted to support him.
I want both his diet and love to go smoothly.
（The other person in love is,▲高嶺＊＊▲... no way!）
You were telling me about the diet of that boy...
Yes, it looks like it's going well. The goal is to lose 15 kilos and he achieved 8 kilos.
Isn't the power of love really amazing?
...I wonder if I should do a diet...
What are you saying so suddenly. Aren't you fine that way?
Only 7 kilos left... If he succeeds, I tell you a secret, okay?
Hey, listen? The story about the boy working hard on his diet, we found a great fact.
There seems that was another girl do a diet in the same class, right? I think it was about her.
That so, I see... That was it... I see...
Mutual love. Isn't it quick somehow?
Recently, it's hard to stay at home on my days off...
... You know? Papa and Mama are very close.
Hmm, how do I say it? I'm happy, but also embarrassed.
Like they can't stand with each other?
Ah~, that's what it feels like! I can't say it... How can I say it?
Are your father and mother lovey-dovey as usual?
Haha. Are you jealous of them?
Certainly, it may be though every day.
It's a lot better than getting along, but I want them to think about their daughter a little.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, are they still showing off?
And that girls loves being lovey-dovey outside.
...Yes. So I wonder if I can say such a thing?
I wonder if the daughter will do it. I'm kidding.
Hey, I thought about it, but Papa and Mama returned to normal.
Wow. Did they notice your line of sight,▲高嶺＊＊▲?
Geez, don't say it like I'm a peeper.
Haha, sorry. But why did they go back?
I don't know. They used to be all lovey-dovey a while ago, but suddenly they got embarrassed.
I think that was something that only Papa and Mama could understand.
Yes... But it's nice to be in love even when old?
Aiming to become a wife, Takane?
Beyond that, Mr. and Mrs. Takane! Fufu!
I wonder if you slept in a strange position, or your pillow.
It may be my pillow. It may be not suitable because have been using it for long, since it was my favorite.
My grandma bought it, so that's it.
But I should change it soon.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ seems to have a good selection）
By the way, what happened with your pillow? Did you buy a new one?
Not yet. I went to a department store, but I couldn't find a similar one.
But, you know? When consulted with the clerk, he tould me it was custom made.
I heard a lot of explanations and it was interesting, so I decided to try it.
Nice! The same pillow as you,▲高嶺＊＊▲...
The custom-made pillow we spoke before, how do you make it?
Height, shape... You can choose the material yourself. I'm worried because I have more freedom.
I have to make a decision quickly...
I see... Do you want to use one? Want to see?
I was worried but, did you order your pillow?
I see. Are you looking forward to it?
Yes▼ If I feel comfortable, can I recommend it to you?
Please! Then, until it arrives, is it arrives, is it okay to lend you my lap?
It would feel bad to receive a lap pillow from a man! Haha!
No, nothing! Pillow is not arriving yet..
Hey, have you ever seen dream come true?
A dream, huh... And you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
My family has always favored soy sauce, right? In a dream Mama said "I'm going to have white miso!"
That was the dream? I wonder if it wasn't because New Year's night.
Fufu, maybe. So, I thought it was impossible and went to the kitchen...
Yes. I was really surprised, but it's a waste, isn't it? That's why I wanted other dream to come true.
By the way, about the story about dreams last time.
Yes, about my dream of white miso.
Is there anything like a trick? How to change our dreams.
I wonder how? But, when I wanted to have a good dream, after doing a lot of things, was that dream.
A picture of a treasure ship, put it under the pillow, write down a spell, or read a book about dreams.
As expected of you,▲高嶺＊＊▲, it's authentic.
Is something wrong? It's not a lucky dream, but a dream.
But the ozoni ingredient was eggplant! Isn't that luck?
Ah~, I'm sorry. Right now I'm talking about ozoni in my dream...
Speaking of which. Did something happen in the year you dreamed of miso and eggplant?
...I want to have a good dream again.
It's about our talk of our dreams from last time...
...It's because it doesn't turn into a dream come true before I talk to you.
Don't you have the same dream?
Imitate? Hmm... What about you,▲高嶺＊＊▲?
I can imitate a Pro- wrestler, you know?
Emm? Um, from the same class... My rival.
Ah, as an example... Yes, I see. Right.
...Did you think I leaned it from a boy?
Your jealousy makes me happy... I'm kidding▼
I forgot it! My pro-wrestler impersonation!
...I wish you showed me something first.
Too bad. I'll show you my imitation next time, okay?
▲高嶺＊＊▲. You told me the other day about imitations, but...
! That is, if you don't do it first――.
Antony Enoki's Manet! Okay, now it's your turn,▲高嶺＊＊▲!
...Um? I would be happy if you could wait for a while...
By the way... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, did you buy something new for your imitation?
Um... don't you know about the guy from a famous quiz show? Everyone says it's similar...
（...Isn't this a new frontier for▲高嶺＊＊▲?）
Hey. How can eyedrops be used correctly?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, don't you know how to use them?
Each time, Papa or me have to help her.
I think so too, but for some reason I don't want to tell Mama.
Hmm...Why? I don't know, it's strange.
Your mother didn't liked it, I suppose.
Yes. I heard that I would put a fist on the cheekbones and use it as a support, so I immediately taught her.
But when Mama does it, she does in on her nose...
Is she scared and avoids her face?
Yes, it seems so. I closed my eyes and said that I will do my best, but before that I ran out of eye drops.
Mama got a little better at using eye drops.
Yes. Mama's happy, but Papa is in a bad mood over it.
Fufu. Maybe because he finds it cute?
Why would he find it cute?
What happened with your mother and the eye drops?
Yes. It seems that Mama noticed Papa's bad mood.
It was cute. But, do you understand?
Papa likes to give Mama her eye drops.
Do you remember the story about the dogs in the neighborhood I told you?
It was the one when you couldn't sleep,▲高嶺＊＊▲?
Yes, I was able to meet with you after a while.
Do you remember that? No way!
I don't remember it. I'm kidding.
But, we got to get along quickly, right? Next time, I want to take a walk.
